{"tid":2029514,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"六合彩110日無再攪珠，獎券基金嗰二百幾億拎晒去all in匯豐 原油 定海洋公園？","createTime":"2020-05-22T09:16:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-23T10:14:11.000Z","uid":7439,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"3e3d524f4664d944e8c2b673393383dbc1b14fc9","tid":2029514,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T09:16:55.000Z","msg":"獎券基金有幾多$$$？<br />\n<blockquote><a href=\"https://www.legco.gov.hk/yr19-20/chinese/counmtg/papers/cm20191127-sp059-c.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.legco.gov.hk%2Fyr19-20%2Fchinese%2Fcounmtg%2Fpapers%2Fcm20191127-sp059-c.pdf&d=SoQ3z30fPgPyNEU4M2c%2BSgESYyyjRTN6W0WnX97q4IQ%3D&h=c36bf231\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.legco.gov.hk/yr19-20/chinese/counmtg/papers/cm20191127-sp059-c.pdf</a><br />\n年終結餘 23,861,961(千元)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.budget.gov.hk/2019/chi/pdf/c-lot.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.budget.gov.hk%2F2019%2Fchi%2Fpdf%2Fc-lot.pdf&d=SoQ3z30fPgPyNEU4M2c%2BSgESYyyjRTN6W0WnX97q4IQ%3D&h=f7676570\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.budget.gov.hk/2019/chi/pdf/c-lot.pdf</a><br />\n該基金截至二零二零年三月三十一日止的預算結餘為 2 2 , 8 7 4 , 0 3 4 , 0 0 0 元，可供應付日後的開支。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n六合彩又唔搞，直接瓜分每人起碼袋住3000蚊先<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，紓民困呀屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nff系列 - 想瓜分獎券基金嗰238億<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1898993\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1898993</a>"},{"pid":"d712aaac835d11f35dc29cd79811292185e7c011","tid":2029514,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T09:18:34.000Z","msg":"馬會在回覆查詢時表示，截至4月26日，疫情期間共取消38場六合彩攪珠，<span style=\"color: red;\">投注額較去年同期減少約18億元，料對獎券基金的撥款減少約2.7億元。</span><br />\n<br />\n1965年成立的獎券基金，旨在支持及發展本港社會福利服務提供財政資助，其收益主要來自六合彩獎券及車牌拍賣，並由社署負責管理。根據特區政府年度賬目，2018/2019財政年度共有11.9億元六合彩收益撥入獎券基金，佔基金收入51%，投資收入則佔45%，其餘4%來自車牌拍賣的淨收入及補助金退款。截至去年3月31日，基金共有238.6億元結存。<br />\n<br />\n受疫情影響，今年2月1日後暫無再舉辦六合彩攪珠。財經事務及庫務局在回覆查詢時表示，<span style=\"color: red;\">今年1月份中下旬及2月1日的六合彩攪珠合共約4,000萬元收益撥入獎券基金，至於2019/2020年度基金的實際結存仍在擬備中。</span><br />\n<br />\n除了獎券基金直接受影響外，平日無論是賽馬、足智彩抑或六合彩，馬會均會將95%稅後經營盈餘撥捐馬會慈善信託基金。六合彩暫停，加上疫情一度令全球足球賽事暫停，至近日才有零星球賽復辦並受注，慈善信託基金亦輕微受影響。<br />\n<br />\n根據馬會年報，2018/2019年度（馬會財政年度為每年6月30日止）慈善信託基金共有43.3億元來自馬會集團的捐款，結餘達366億元。<br />\n<br />\n馬會發言人表示，為支援社區應對疫情所帶來的挑戰，馬會自2月起至今共批出3.46億元捐款，包括直接向社區捐出或捐助購買逾1,400萬個口罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />；先後成立1億元「緊急援助基金」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />和1.5億元「賽馬會社區持續抗逆基金」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />；向非政府機構<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />提供撥款以支援弱勢社群<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />等，發言人強調：「縱使疫情影響收益，馬會將繼續動用本身資源，貫徹對香港社會的承諾。」"},{"pid":"9905107a9a14d787490ce0d1511084820bf835e9","tid":2029514,"uid":7439,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T09:22:06.000Z","msg":"李芷晴疫情下幾乎失業：無諗過六合彩竟然會停<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/4046289/org/76d91f24e2ed2fad7fb8b8edb73f98d0.jpg/-M1fDXfZz1260qwdqEesxDIMLnFlZ3PJbnVJTG51SUw\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F4046289%2Forg%2F76d91f24e2ed2fad7fb8b8edb73f98d0.jpg%2F-M1fDXfZz1260qwdqEesxDIMLnFlZ3PJbnVJTG51SUw&h=7f3e485b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5a716582e4144dc6a6dae2e46398ca72618f9baa","tid":2029514,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T13:34:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26f22a26b632da806f982e199455a769352de787","tid":2029514,"uid":76078,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9905107a9a14d787490ce0d1511084820bf835e9","tid":2029514,"uid":7439,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"cited